OL,5, Train drivers are "very close" to going
OL,6, on strike and could walk out within    
OL,7, weeks, according to their union.       
OL,9,FDrivers at eight rail companies voted  
OL,10,Fon Monday in favour of industrial      
OL,11,Faction in a row over pay.              
OL,13,FMick Whelan, general secretary of      
OL,14,FAslef, told the BBC that strike action 
OL,15,Fcould happen in the coming weeks if    
OL,16,Ftalks over wage rises stall.           
OL,18,F"We don't do this lightly," he said.   
OL,19,F"We see it as a sign of failure when we
OL,20,Fdo have to do it."                     
